1
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,200
Lin You

2
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:01,840
What are you doing?

3
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,320
Come back, Lin You!

4
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,879
Open the door!

5
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,160
Lao Wang

6
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,640
Forgive me for what I said earlier.

7
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,920
Zhou Yi should be in surgery now.

8
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,920
He's going to be okay.

9
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:16,640
Also,

10
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,440
the police should be here soon.

11
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,880
I put the evidence in your pocket.

12
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,360
Remember to hand it over.

13
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:24,120
Once you get the compensation,

14
00:01:24,320 --> 00:01:26,360
find a better place for Daji.

15
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,200
Brat.

16
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,520
What nonsense is this?

17
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:31,000
Get over here right now!

18
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:33,640
No, Lin You!

19
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:35,680
Lin You, what are you saying?

20
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,440
Open the door, hurry!

21
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,760
I order you to open this door now!

22
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:41,640
With that tone of yours,

23
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,520
no one will push you around again.

24
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:45,840
Don't worry.

25
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,360
I won't die.

26
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,280
Didn't you say I have a strong fate?

27
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,320
No!

28
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,200
Go home and wait for me, Master.

29
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,200
Uncle Wang.

30
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,360
I've brought your lamp back for you.

31
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,560
It's at Sister Bai's place.

32
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,320
I know you can light it up.

33
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:00,760
No!

34
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:03,400
Brat, you'd better keep your word!

35
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,120
We'll be waiting for you.

36
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:08,720
All of you, back off!

37
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,600
Get lost!

38
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,520
Lin You!

39
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,440
Lin You, don't go!

40
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:22,680
Lin You, don't go!

41
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,160
Come back, Lin You!

42
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,360
Don't go! Open the door!

43
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,960
Lin You, don't go!

44
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:33,440
I'm begging you, come back, Lin You!

45
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,480
I'm begging you.

46
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:39,560
Master, do something, Master!

47
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:45,680
Lin You.

48
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,360
Why do you always betray me?

49
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:50,600
Always standing against me,

50
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,480
just for a crazy old man

51
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,440
and a lunatic?

52
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,760
I've been right here.

53
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,280
You're the one who went to the other side.

54
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,720
Look at yourself right now.

55
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,880
What's the difference between you

56
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,920
and the people who used to bully us?

57
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,400
You clearly had a choice.

58
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,520
I made my choice.

59
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,200
But what about them?

60
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,800
Did they ever let us go?

61
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:21,000
If Lao Wang had been the one being hunted

62
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,680
and you were the one inside,

63
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,400
would you have opened the door?

64
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:26,560
Of course.

65
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,840
Then add to that

66
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,360
me, with a heart condition,

67
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,120
on the brink of life and death?

68
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,960
You're still defending them?

69
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,680
But that's the truth.

70
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,040
Have you ever really thought

71
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,480
about what I actually want?

72
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,720
I made a mistake.

73
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,800
I don't want to make any more mistakes.

74
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,960
I don't want you to make the same mistakes.

75
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,320
If you really cared how I felt,

76
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,880
you wouldn't force me

77
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,320
to hurt the people I care about.

78
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:07,840
Bro.

79
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,800
Do you have to push yourself to a dead end?

80
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,640
What have I forced you into?

81
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,400
I'm your brother.

82
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,360
I'm the one who's your brother.

83
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,160
What kind of family are they?

84
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:27,080
Everything you ate and used as a kid,

85
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,360
I bought it all.

86
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,560
I stole and robbed to give you what you wanted.

87
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:34,400
I'd even give you my life if you wanted it.

88
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,400
You wanted to live in that building across the way,

89
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,680
and I made it happen for you.

90
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:40,760
And you?

91
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:43,000
Why are you backing out?

92
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,560
Why did you betray me?

93
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,480
Bro.

94
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,920
Do you really care about me?

95
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,600
I'm just an excuse for your revenge.

96
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,320
Stop fooling yourself.

97
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,000
Turn yourself in.

98
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,640
If you keep going down this path alone,

99
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,760
we will no longer be brothers.

100
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,560
I told you,

101
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,760
as long as I'm here,

102
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,800
you can't touch Daji.

103
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,440
You've made your choice.

104
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,280
Fine then.

105
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,960
Let's end this once and for all.

106
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,960
Whatever you do, I'll forgive you.

107
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,120
Bro promises you.

108
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,560
There will come a day

109
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,640
when Bro takes all those people

110
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,840
who've bullied us all these years

111
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,160
and knocks every one of them down

112
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:17,880
right under our feet.

113
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:22,760
Come on, bring it on!

114
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,640
Lin You!

115
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,440
Lin You!

116
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,040
Why did you do this?

117
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,880
Someone!

118
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,000
Someone, help!

119
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,680
Call an ambulance!

120
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,760
- Call an ambulance! - Yes, sir!

121
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,840
Don't be afraid.

122
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,920
Bro's here.

123
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,240
Bro...

124
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,760
Do you remember,

125
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,440
when we were little,

126
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,680
back when we were kids,

127
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,560
when we went to the bathhouse,

128
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,200
I complained that when you scrubbed,

129
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,600
the back scrub hurt.

130
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:34,760
Only now do I realize,

131
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,640
that pain,

132
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,840
it's also,

133
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,360
a kind of love.

134
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:44,640
Bro,

135
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,120
you are,

136
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,000
in this lifetime,

137
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,040
the closest family I'll ever have.

138
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,080
Liu Liu and the others too.

139
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,800
Between family,

140
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:59,360
we can't hurt each other.

141
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,680
Bro...

142
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,240
Bro's right here.

143
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,000
I'm begging you,

144
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:11,240
don't stay trapped in the past anymore.

145
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,240
I made mistakes.

146
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,320
I know that.

147
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,240
I was too young back then.

148
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:23,560
I don't want my own family,

149
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,680
to pay the same price again.

150
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,000
Lin You.

151
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,360
Don't talk, okay?

152
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,280
Bro... Bro...

153
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,360
I'm going home.

154
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,480
I can see home.

155
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,320
You...

156
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,240
You're there too.

157
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,160
You're there too.

158
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,760
Lin You!

159
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,240
Lin You!

160
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:06,320
Lin You!

161
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,400
You!

162
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,520
Don't scare Bro.

163
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:12,880
Look at Bro.

164
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,720
Just look at Bro!

165
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:18,840
You...

166
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,280
Bro was wrong.

167
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,360
Let's go home.

168
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:26,920
Bro will go home with you.

169
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,720
We'll live like normal people.

170
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:32,400
Live an ordinary, simple life.

171
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,080
You...

172
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,520
Lin You, look at Bro.

173
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,800
You!

174
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,440
You'll be okay.

175
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:57,960
You'll be okay.

176
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:08,120
I've never believed in you.

177
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,520
I've never begged you either.

178
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:15,120
I'm begging you, save my brother.

179
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:17,080
I'm the one who did all the bad things.

180
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,600
It has nothing to do with my brother.

181
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,560
I'm begging you, save my brother.

182
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,400
Please, I beg you.

183
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,360
Please, I beg you.

184
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,880
I'm willing to give a life for a life.

185
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,000
As long as you...

186
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,680
can make sure my brother...

187
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,560
can make sure my brother is okay,

188
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,840
I'm willing to give a life for a life.

189
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:24,920
Save...

190
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:27,760
Save...

191
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,920
my brother.

192
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,280
Grandma.

193
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:54,960
What does family really mean?

194
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:57,360
Would family ever give up on family?

195
00:11:59,040 --> 00:11:59,840
Child,

196
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,520
family is who you choose.

197
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,000
Whoever you choose,

198
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:06,000
that person becomes your family.

199
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,840
I believe in you.

200
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,920
You must've had no choice.

201
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,320
Take good care and recover.

202
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,720
Lao Wang will be fine.

203
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:42,920
Lin You.

204
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:46,000
You're not such a bad guy.

205
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,480
How long has he been sitting there?

206
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,800
He's been like that since he got here.

207
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:08,200
Brother Wang.

208
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,120
I'm back.

209
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:14,640
The reason I didn't come to see you before

210
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,520
is because, actually,

211
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:19,280
we don't blame you.

212
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:20,560
Besides,

213
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,560
you've taken great care of Zhou Yi,

214
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:26,000
the one we cared about most.

215
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:30,960
So,

216
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:34,560
what reason do we have to stay?

217
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,480
Thank you, child.

218
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,400
Lao Wang.

219
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,640
The lamp lit up, didn't it?

220
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:57,840
Excuse me,

221
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,640
is this the Daji agency?

222
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,360
How can I help you?

223
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:12,000
I'm looking for a job.

224
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,560
And a place to stay, too.

225
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,120
Come on in, let's talk.

226
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:17,440
The pay's negotiable.

227
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:20,600
As for rent...

228
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:21,920
Welcome back.
